'''神经肌肉接点'''（英文：Neuromuscular junction），又称'''神经肌肉接觸面，'''是[[传出神经纤维|传出神经纤维]]与[[肌肉纖維|肌肉纤维]]之间的化学联络点，连接[[运动神经元|运动神经元]]和[[肌肉細胞|肌肉细胞]]，与[[神经元|神经元]]之间的[[突触|突触]]功能相同<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Motor Neuron-Muscle Relationships|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK10816/|last=Purves|first=Dale|last2=Augustine|first2=George J.|date=2001|journal=Neuroscience. 2nd edition|language=en|last3=Fitzpatrick|first3=David|last4=Katz|first4=Lawrence C.|last5=LaMantia|first5=Anthony-Samuel|last6=McNamara|first6=James O.|last7=Williams|first7=S. Mark|access-date=2021-03-06|archive-date=2021-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210409133354/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK10816/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|chapter=Physiology, Neuromuscular Junction|title=StatPearls|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK470413/|publisher=StatPearls Publishing|date=2021|location=Treasure Island (FL)|pmid=29261907|first=Abdillahi|last=Omar|first2=Komal|last2=Marwaha|first3=Pradeep C.|last3=Bollu|access-date=2021-03-06|archive-date=2021-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210409133320/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK470413/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Neuromuscular Junction - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/medicine-and-dentistry/neuromuscular-junction|accessdate=2021-03-06|work=|publisher=Science Direct|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210409133406/https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/medicine-and-dentistry/neuromuscular-junction|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[神经纤维|神经纤维]]分为许多末梢分支，每个分支嵌入肌[[细胞膜|细胞膜]]上称为[[運動终板|運動终板]]的凹陷中。终板内容纳数以千计的受体（长形的[[蛋白质|蛋白质]]分子，形成穿过膜的通道）。

